thank you for downloading our project!
here are the steps to make it run.
1. go to https://www.mailgun.com/ and make a free account
2. add the email addresses you wish to use for the group communication feature
3. accept the verification email you receive in each inbox respectively
4. add your mailgun api key and domain name to the .env-replace-me file
5. rename ".env-replace-me" to ".env"
6. install nodejs
7. run "npm install"
8. run "npm start"
9. the server should now be running!
